lead_paragraph: Denver Broncos coach Gary Kubiak has named Trevor Siemian the starting quarterback for Week One, when the defending champions open the 2016 season with a rematch of Super Bowl 50.

headline.print_headline: Quarterback Siemian to Start for Broncos
